Load Balancer (HAProxy Cluster): HAProxy, configured as a cluster, serves as a backup for the other load balancer. It distributes incoming traffic across multiple servers, ensuring even load distribution, fault tolerance, and high availability.

Having different component on different servers evades the issue of the vulnerability of one component affecting the other.
